OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Fmostly cloudy overnight and turning
OL,7,Frather murky too, especially in the
OL,8,Fsouth and east. Patchy rain arriving
OL,9,Fover Northern Ireland and western
OL,10,FScotland by morning. A mostly mild
OL,11,Fnight.
