OL,13,CTuesday:FCloudy again for most, rain
OL,14,Fin the west slowly moving east and
OL,15,Fweakening. Winds increasing through
OL,16,Fthe day, breaking up the cloud.
OL,17,FFurther rain arriving in the west by
OL,18,Fevening.
